channel.description:
ok i downloaded a scar script from www.sythe.org and i got this error.
Line 363: [Error] (15177:1): Unknown identifier 'antiban' in script C:\windows\TEMP\Rar$DI02.098\PowerwoodCutter V2.2.scar
anyone any ideas? i tried taking that out, then it took me to the next line, which the error is: Line 363: [Error] (15177:1): Unknown identifier 'HoverEvery' in script C:\windows\TEMP\Rar$DI02.098\PowerwoodCutter V2.2.scar
any ideas =[[ please?
P.S i re-added antiban;
